author: Kate McCann
title: Amber Rudd says her bid to force energy price cut is 'not over yet'
text: Politics Amber Rudd says her bid to force energy price cut is 'not over yet' The Energy Secretary vowed to put pressure on the big six to cut their gas and electricity prices as winter approaches Amber Rudd, the Energy Secretary, has promised to put pressure on big companies to cut their prices Photo: PA By Kate McCann , Senior Political Correspondent 6:31PM BST 15 Oct 2015
